---
title: Saucy Tex-Mex Chicken & Potato Top Pie with Cauliflower & Corn
description: Tonight, let’s turn juicy chicken in a creamy corn and veggie sauce into a delicious potato-top pie. You can smell the Tex-Mex
seasoning as it bakes - that’s when dinner gets very exciting, so dig in and enjoy!
